name: DayBreak Diffusion
description:
Welocome Day Break Diffusion

Former name: umisemixv3

This model is a remix of umisemixv2 and v3, a block weight marge of over 50 models, and further re-trained.

It is a model that can be precisely adapted to various patterns and depictions, and you can add your own patterns from here.

Recommended settings

clip skip: 2

Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras or Eular a

number of steps: The more steps, the more detailed the model.
